imdb.title: Flushed
plot: FLUSHED is a brand new, rip-roaring game show for kids. On a set unlike any other, two teams of two battle it out to determine who wins the prize and who ends up covered in PURPLE SLUDGE.
synopsis: Flushed is a brand new, rip- roaring game show for kids. On a set unlike any other, two teams of two battle it out to determine who wins the prize and who ends up covered in purple sludge!The teams first answer fun questions to build time on the clock. Then the teams race against the clock and each other to complete their link. Tubes connect together from an outlet to the team inlet in the center of the stage. The winner goes on the leader board, while their opponents are now trapped inside the sludge tank, with a gigantic vat of purple sludge hanging precariously above them. All that's left is to crank the lever and flush them!FLUSHED is the show that's got everybody talking and kids all over the country can't decide if they want to win or want to get FLUSHED!You'll be laughing with and cheering for our teams as they put their general knowledge and strategy skills to the ultimate test. Featuring a massive, interactive set, energetic sound track and stunning 3D graphics, 'FLUSHED' is a one of a kind game show that everyone wants to play!
